divs: Sighting DetailsI was in my back garden and I just looked upwards, I thought they were 2 stars at first but realised they were moving. These 2 object were on the same level and heading towards each other. they then crossed paths, there were no tails behind them, just 2 star looking objects. my 1st thoughts they were going to collide, but they did not and just passed each other...one of them then faded and the other came to a standstill and stayed motionless after that and just looked like a star in the sky.
Summary: 2 star like objects crossed pathed then one faded away
